ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 209, Quebec
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 209 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of QUEBEC, with respect to the spring floods that occurred from April 5 to June 2, 2017, which affected many communities.
